room_title: Escape room "Pirate Booty" by Escape Room Park City in Salt Lake City
room_description:
Aye, the Pirate Booty where there be plenty treasure, but ye must find yer way home before ye can escape. 
Fun for all ages, this room has it all, treasure, pirates, games, puzzles and cannon balls, don't forget the cannon balls. Everyone loves this room!
